data.eml:eml: Two new dragonflies (Odonata: Anisoptera) from the Miocene of Carinthia (Austria)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Schädel, Mario, Lechner, Thomas S. (2017): Two new dragonflies (Odonata: Anisoptera) from the Miocene of Carinthia (Austria). Zootaxa 4243 (1): 153-164, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4243.1.7
